docker-compose build
docker-compose up -d
docker exec -it dind-container /bin/sh

To verify CNTR:
--------------
 cntr --version

To verify FSUE:
--------------
mkdir -p /mnt/fuse-test/lower /mnt/fuse-test/upper /mnt/fuse-test/work /mnt/fuse-test/merged
echo "Hello, FUSE!" > /mnt/fuse-test/upper/testfile.txt
fuse-overlayfs -o lowerdir=/mnt/fuse-test/lower,upperdir=/mnt/fuse-test/upper,workdir=/mnt/fuse-test/work /mnt/fuse-test/merged
ls /mnt/fuse-test/merged

# Clean up

umount -l /mnt/fuse-test/merged
rm -rf /mnt/fuse-test


Running with SLIM:
------------------

    cd workspace/
    docker build -t slim-sqlite -f Dockerfile.slim . # Runs appx. 40s
    docker run -d --name slim-sqlite slim-sqlite

    phoronix-test:
    -------------
    docker exec -it slim-sqlite phoronix-test-suite batch-setup # To save settings (Y,n,n,n,n,n,Y)
    ./run_slim_tests.sh

    sqlite-test:
    -------------
    docker exec slim-sqlite /usr/bin/time -v /workload.sh > ./slim_results/slim_sqlite.log 2>&1


With SLIM + FAT (with debugging tools):
---------------------------------------

    docker build -t fat-debug -f Dockerfile.fat .  # Runs appx. 55s
    docker run -d --name fat-debug fat-debug
    cntr attach slim-sqlite fat-debug

    phoronix-test:
    -------------
    ./run_fat_tests.sh

    sqlite-test:
    -------------
    docker exec slim-sqlite /usr/bin/time -v /workload.sh > ./slim_fat_results/slim_with_fat.log 2>&1


Dcoker Cleanup:

    ./clean.sh



Other docker commands:

    docker stop <container>
    docker rm <container>


